  "triggerCount": 0,
  "notes": "RIS Orchestrator with 3 independent paths:\nPath A: Health Monitor (every 30min) - research-health + research-stats, Discord alert if RED/CRITICAL/FAIL\nPath B: Manual Pipeline Trigger (POST /webhook/ris-trigger) - switch on pipeline param, executes sub-workflows\nPath C: URL Ingest (POST /webhook/ris-ingest) - research-acquire with url+source_family\nREQUIRES: DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL in n8n environment variables for Path A alerts.\nMUTUAL EXCLUSION: Do NOT activate Path B sub-workflow triggers while APScheduler is running.\nSee docs/adr/0013-ris-n8n-pilot-scoped.md for scope boundaries."
}
